io.jenkins.plugins.logintheme.LoginTheme.head:
<style>
html {
  font: Helvetica;
  color: #3f3f40;
}

.simple-page form {
   width: unset;
   max-width: unset;
}

.simple-page .jenkins-input {
  width: 90%
}

.simple-page form input {
  outline: none !important;
  color: #3f3f40;
  border: solid 1px #ee9b00; /*var(--main-bg-color-focus);*/
  
}

.simple-page form input:focus {
  outline: none !important;
  border: solid 1px #ee9b00; /*var(--main-bg-color-focus);*/
  box-shadow: 0 0 15px #ee9b00;
}

.simple-page #loginIntroDefault img {
  display: none;
}

.simple-page #loginIntroDefault h1 {
  display: none;
}

.simple-page .submit-button {
  outline: none !important;
  color: #3f3f40 !important;
  border: solid 1px #ee9b00; /*var(--main-bg-color-focus);*/
  background-color: #ee9b00 !important;
}

.Checkbox input[type="checkbox"]:checked + .Checkbox-indicator {
  background-color: #ee9b00 !important;
  border-color: #ee9b00 !important;
}

/* This is the OCD3 login page logo */
.simple-page .logo {
  height: 120px;
  margin: -10px;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-position: 50% 0;
  background-size: 100%;
  background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,);

}
</style>
